    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2017 Shelby GT350, a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. This specimen features the 5.2L 'Voodoo' V8 with its signature flat-plane crankshaft, delivering an 8,250 RPM redline through a Tremec TR-3160 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis is equipped with the MagneRide Damping System and a Torsen 3.73 limited-slip differential, providing exceptional lateral grip and mechanical feedback. This vehicle has been maintained in a climate-controlled environment with a flawless service record, ensuring the Brembo braking system and forged internals remain in peak operational state. No track sessions or modifications; strictly OE-spec throughout.",
