    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age and stands as a benchmark for the model. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its original showroom luster. The exterior paint is flawless, free of any stone chips or swirls, and has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of bolster wear, and the interior retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component and accessory functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with every service performed on time and documented by authorized specialists. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line\u2014tight, responsive, and incredibly smooth. Included with the sale are all original keys, the complete set of owner\u2019s manuals, and a comprehensive binder of service records. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning enthusiast to acquire a showroom-quality example that has been cared for with an open checkbook.",
      "price": 48500.0,
